{"tid":1633484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求各位，可唔可以貼返，蘇聯點分化敵方條link出黎","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:20:58.000Z","uid":73392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b21ca9243dfacba0adf0ca29fbe5639bca594b00","tid":1633484,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:13:32.000Z","msg":"依加嘅情況同個post講嘅，完全一模一樣，d 打手瘋狂推post，佢地唔至會推對政府有利嘅post，同時仲會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">瘋狂推對示威者有利嘅</span>post，你冇睇錯係推對我方有利嘅post，姐係兩邊都推，目的就係將示威一方分化<br />\n<br />\n例如，有人狂推等人權法過左女，先大裝修<br />\n同時，有人推政府就輸，要立刻裝修<br />\n<br />\n令示威者冇曬方向，我想同大家講，唔好太理連登post講咩，呢個只係平台，唔係大台，大家要獨立思考，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住不論做咩，都不割席，不分化</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">太過份就係鬼做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"823833a40210e0e12af1145ad155bc6f18652c73","tid":1633484,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e2ae1de66304fd8e47d3b01debc6d1d0e29fe00","tid":1633484,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7b6ec98e96756d07a190e670f64c788f4195c66","tid":1633484,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a107bf882c5dfe524be6ef68cd20ea538572f7e4","tid":1633484,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:17:24.000Z","msg":"幫手推下啦，想搵返個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4de1f90c9c0c6045df65eb42a4cb7f91855a2f7","tid":1633484,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse